    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car is in pristine, showroom-ready condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one! It\u2019s incredibly clean, runs like a charm, and still has that fresh feel you usually only find at the dealership. I\u2019m really sad to see it go, but I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it as much as I do. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
