    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like luster and absolutely no chips, swirls, or imperfections. Every body panel aligns perfectly, and the factory-spec wheels are free of even the slightest curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather remains supple and matte, devoid of any creasing or wear, and still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the ambient lighting, functions with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive, documented service history with every maintenance milestone performed exclusively by certified technicians. Garage-kept under a breathable cover and never driven in inclement weather, this vehicle offers the rare experience of buying a 'new' classic. It drives with the tight, responsive feel of a car that just left the assembly line.",
      "price": 45500.0,
